{"tid":670543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"專業巧手彷妝化身「蒙娜麗莎」「鄧麗君」  網友驚嘆畫作化為現實","createTime":"2018-05-19T12:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T05:59:17.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca53c9f449ecc279b08ae5cd4ce2d3552f8d13f1","tid":670543,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"一個重慶女孩YUYA模仿達文西名畫《蒙娜麗莎》妝容的短片，近日在內地網上瘋傳，網民看後驚嘆簡直是真人版的「蒙娜麗莎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/2018-05-17_23-39-51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F2018-05-17_23-39-51.jpg&h=536e2337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYUYA（左圖）化身的「蒙娜麗莎」<br />\n<br />\n這位被網民稱為「仿妝大神」的YUYA是個美妝博主，今年27歲。網上流傳短片但見她手法熟練，從全素顏，到打粉底、唇部遮瑕、修容、高光、陰影，一步步從一個純亞洲人的臉變成了世界名畫。<br />\n<br />\n扮作鄧麗君維肖維妙<br />\n<br />\nYUYA表示，這次仿妝「蒙娜麗莎」的靈感來自粉絲。「有粉絲開玩笑說我長得像蒙娜麗莎，我就突發奇想是不是可以試一下。」YUYA說：「我從10點化到下午4點，做了很多準備，沒想到這麼受歡迎。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/2018-05-17_23-39-55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F2018-05-17_23-39-55.jpg&h=d7242dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仿妝達文西的名畫《抱貂女郎》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/2018-05-17_23-39-57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F2018-05-17_23-39-57.jpg&h=95012ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n模仿鄧麗君<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2012-LEGCO.LONGHAIR.1200.2103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2012-LEGCO.LONGHAIR.1200.2103.jpg&h=89ed2504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n模仿梁國雄<br />\n<br />\n原來，除了蒙娜麗莎，YUYA還扮過達文西另一幅名畫《抱貂女郎》，亦是「神還原」。她又扮過鄧麗君、林允，甚至男明星鹿晗，堪稱百變女神。"},{"pid":"37fa8eb6383a188dbcf997086475670ad091288c","tid":670543,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾"},{"pid":"69ce3fb0f58277c5379a91b14ab55d3d0876ff28","tid":670543,"uid":3189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/4b/MmZbg.gif/revision/latest?cb=20130818143318\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F4b%2FMmZbg.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130818143318&h=1bafdd1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b4546b3beafe8fbce72463656b4487de34861c4","tid":670543,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"梁國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}